	n R&B\, in a room full of people with your same taste in music. We can't w
	ait to see you all on tour. Box Opens: 7:00 Doors: 8:00 This is a 21+ even
	t. Must have valid ID for entry.\nNoise Complaints Presents: The Late Nigh
	t R&B Experience Tour What started as a YouTube series has now become a na
	tionwide movement. Now we're bringing it live to a city near you. An eveni
	ng of classic and modern R&B\, in a room full of people with your same tas
