UID:xcdbo7G5JoJlTY_8aTd8s
SUMMARY:Painting with Plants
DTSTAMP:20260619T133504Z
DTSTART:20260725T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:$37 member / $52 nonmemberAges 12+\, all minors must be accompa
	nied by an adult \n\n\n\nYou’ve tried watercolors\, oils\, and acrylics\, 
	but have you ever tried daisies? In this fun\, relaxed class we’ll explore
	 the fascinating world of natural pigments. Learn which plants make which 
	colors as you create a watercolor-style artwork to take home. All supplies
	 will be provided – just bring your creativity. \n\n\n\nPlease dress for t
	he weather and wear clothes you don’t mind getting messy. \n\n\n\n\nsold o
	ut\n\nhttps://houstonarboretum.org/event/painting-with-plants/\n\nFrom Hou
	ston Arboretum & Nature Center
URL:https://houstonarboretum.org/event/painting-with-plants/
